<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="23Jul1925"><font color="red">23 July 1925</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver): Escorted by three thunder storms we arrived here the day before yesterday. I have been looking round for a suitable place but have not found one yet. The address I gave will be good for a few days. </div>
